profile_positions.description:
As Strategic Portfolio Manager I am responsible for developing strategic masterplans of the corporate real estate portfolio for own use of ING worldwide (both leasehold and freehold). I advise our local business units on real estate processes, with a focus on optimising the real estate to deliver an added value to the core business and I'm responsible the the execution of the Masterplans that are defined dureing the advisory phase.
I manage and support local team and report frequently to Board of Management on the proceeds and results of the project.
My current projects are:
•	Strategic repositioning freehold real estate portfolio Netherlands;
ING is centralising business activities in The Netherlands to the Amsterdam region, over time our regional head offices will be faced with structural vacancy. To avoid vacancy issues and to create a new future for these office buildings, we are pro-active in defining redevelopment scenarios and marketing the redevelopment plans to interested developers. Furthermore we are in the process with local government to create maximum zoning plan freedom.
-	Haarlemmerweg Amsterdam (60.000 m2)
-	Financial Plaza Amsterdam (40.000 m2)
-	Velperweg Arnhem (75.000 m2)
-	Leeuwarden (80.000 m2)
•	Master plan Milan – Italy; 
Acquisition of a Pre-lease for new Head quarter (10.000 m2) for ING in Milan.
•	Master plan Luxemburg - Luxembourg;
Acquisition of a Pre-lease for new Head quarter (13.000 m2) in the inner city of Luxembourg. Simultaneously disposing ING’s current three freehold head quarters in Luxembourg.
•	Master plan Frankfurt – Germany;
Acquisition of a Pre-lease for new Head quarter (50.000 m2) for ING in Frankfurt. 
My completed projects are:
•	Master plan Warsaw – Poland;
Acquisition of pre-lease for new Head quarter (13.000 m2) in Warsaw.
•	Master plan Toronto – Canada;
Define Master plan and analyse business needs for future head quarter strategy in Toronto.

As projectdeveloper I was responsible for the entire development project from acquisition to completion.

My projects:
* Leerpark Dordrecht
Leerpark is an integral area development of living, working and learning; 
* Deelplan 16 Ypenburg – De Hollandsche Meesters
Aread evelopment 150 familyhouses and 71 land plots for private development;
* Deelplan De Dijken Leidschenveen
Area development 200 familyhouses and 30 apartments;
* Knowledge group Living;
* Startlab, conceptdevelopment.
